Package: connector.databricks
Title: Expansion of the connector package for enabling connections to
    databricks
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: c(
    person("Steffen Falgreen", "Larsen", , "sffl@novonordisk.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Aksel", "Thomsen", , "oath@novonordisk.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Novo Nordisk A/S", role = "cph")
  )
Description: Expands the connector package to handle databricks. This
    includes reading and writing of files to volumes as well as
    connections to sparklyr.
